	(text_box "To ensure safety when handling LiPo batteries,\nit is essential to protect against the following risks:\n- Overcurrent during charging\n- Overcurrent during discharging\n- Overvoltage\n- Undervoltage\n- Reverse polarity\n- Short circuits"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 78.74 63.5 0)
