	)
	(text_box "Overcharge detection: 4.28 V\nOver-discharge detection: 2.8 V\nDischarge overcurrent detection: 0.15 V\nCharge overcurrent detection: -0.1 V\nShort-circuit detection: 0.5 V\n\nMaximum desired discharge current is 1.5 A.\nTotal resistance across FETs should be\n0.15 V / 1.5 A = 100 mΩ.\n\nMaximum desired charge current is 1 A.\n100 mΩ * 1 A = 100 mV trigger level.\n\nR_{DS(ON)} @ 2.5 V_{GS} = ~9 mΩ\n9 mΩ * 2 = 18 mΩ\n\nR_{VSS} = 100 mΩ - 18 mΩ = 82 mΩ"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 127 143.51 0)
		(size 48.26 36.83)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
