	(text_box "To ensure compatibility with a wide range of LiPo batteries, set the charging current to 450 mA.\n\nTo visually confirm that charging is in progress and that the battery is being utilized, LEDs will indicate the status according to the \"STATUS OUTPUTS\" table."
